The,Yahoo,Status,API,allows,for,users,to,set,and,share,their,status,on,Yahoo,and,on,applications,The,user,s,status,is,a,string,with,a,maximum,length,of,characters,anything,longer,will,be,silently,truncated,The,Status,API,filters,unsafe,user,input,to,avoid,security,issues,such,as,invalid,characters,in,a,URL,SQL,injections,or,cross,site,scripting,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML,and,JSON